name: Annunaki The Beginning
description: Annunaki is an adventures saga. This is the first of the three parts proposed. This story is based on an event that took place fifty thousand years from today, most of which is influenced by Sumerian tablets, in this we first know the birth of man and the science or myth behind it. In this, we have our biggest secret, did the aliens give birth to a human whom we call God. This is a unique journey in which we see a new world, the characters of this story meet you with the immense power to fight continuously against the forces of evil. When you purchase this NFT movie script you will also get the bible to this movie. This movie script has never been SOLD it is the Original & it has been copyrighted. WRITTEN BY: WILLIAM NARANJO AND AJAY PAL
